# Deploy (Kamal + GitHub Actions)

- Push to `master`: Brakeman → RuboCop → RSpec → `bin/kamal deploy`.
- Workflow: `.github/workflows/ci.yml`; secrets doc: `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md`.
- CI secrets file: copy `.kamal/secrets.cd` → `.kamal/secrets` (env vars from GitHub Secrets).
- Local deploy: `.kamal/secrets` from `.kamal/secrets.example` (gitignored).
- Health check route: `GET /up`.
- Image: `adam1344/flipflapp_rails`; host: `flipflapp.fr`.
